des:
Search the world's largest crossword dictionary for answers to your crossword clues. The Crossword Solver is the most comprehensive and up-to-date source for Quick, General Knowledge, and Cryptic crossword puzzle answers.

Just say "Tell Crossword Solver the clue is", then say the clue, and Crossword Solver will provide the most relevant answers to your clue. Tell the Crossword Solver how many letters are in your answer and get answers of a certain length. Tell the Crossword Solver about any known letters, for example, eighth letter is 'Y', or first letter is 'W', and Crossword Solver will only give answers with letters in those positions.

Here are a few things to try:
 o Next - Get more answers to the same clue
 o # Letters - limit answers to a certain length
 o Second letter is 'O' - find only answers with letters in the specified position
 o Spell That - spell your answer
 o Wait - when you just need a little more time

There's more! Read the Advanced Help to learn what the Crossword Solver can do: https://www.wordplays.com/alexa-help

The Crossword Solver is brought to you by wordplays.com. Visit Wordplays.com https://www.wordplays.com to solve crossword puzzles, play word games, and solve word puzzles.
